-- Lufthansa Plans 1.5 Billion-Euro Cost Cuts, Handelsblatt Reports
-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 2011-12-21T06:42:52Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-21/lufthansa-plans-1-5-billion-euro-cost-cuts-handelsblatt-reports.html
Deutsche Lufthansa AG (LHA)  may cut costs
by 1.5 billion euros ($2 billion) under a plan that will
probably be presented in March,  Handelsblatt  reported today,
without saying where it obtained the information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
